  "success": true,
  "access": "read"
}
```

### HTTP Request

`PUT <%= api_url %>/api/roles/:id/update-permission`

### JSON Parameters

Parameter | Default | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
permissionCode  |  | The code of the permission being changed
access     |  | The new access level. **full**, **read**, **none**

